{"id":192092,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/澳广-土耳其地震死亡人数接近500/","date":"2011-10-27T20:00:45Z","modified":"2011-10-27T20:00:45Z","title":"澳广 | 土耳其地震死亡人数接近500","content":"<div>\n<p>土耳其地震死亡人数接近500</p>\n<p>土耳其7.2级大地震造成的死亡人数已经接近500人，另外有1600 多人受伤。不过当局警告说，还有数百甚至上千人被埋在了废墟下。.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<p>2011  年 10 月 27 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3349249.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3349249.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3349249.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3349249.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3349249.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3349249.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>土耳其7.2级大地震造成的死亡人数已经接近500人，另外有1600 多人受伤。不过当局警告说，还有数百甚至上千人被埋在了废墟下。</p>\n<p>据当地媒体报道，在经过了震后72小时黄金时期经过去后，再找到生还者的机会变得十分渺茫。</p>\n<p>当地灾民批评政府救灾不力， 灾区物资短缺。据介绍，目前，当地气温骤降。</p>\n<p>地震在上个星期日发生，超过220